AUDIO: 'renders a beautiful image. 40 understands most requests without having to format them with special syntax. Just type what you want. If you want more control over'

[00:50] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'composition or style, you can drag in up to four images as global reference layers. Just drop them into the canvas and then use the prompt box to tell the model how to use them. For example, I can upload a quick sketch and say'

